            <div>
                <opener>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Excuse a hasty letter to beg you would send me the Erse names of the bagpipe with
                    their litteral translation. &amp; get them from somebody versed in the
                    language</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> &amp;c</salute>
                    <signed>
                        <persName ref="pe0232">T Pennant</persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
                <dateline>Jan. 11<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> 1774.</dateline>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>To Mr Paton</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Custom House</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Edinburgh</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <persName ref="pe0015">
                        <hi rend="superscript">Free</hi>RMostyn</persName>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <stamp>
                        <placeName ref="pl0705">NORTHOP</placeName>
                    </stamp>
                </p>
